    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Azoospermia confirmed by two semen analysis (at minimum 74 days between the both
             analysis)

          -  Volume of seminal plasma &gt;0.6ml

          -  Testicular biopsy one month after the last semen analysis

          -  Informed consent signed by the patient

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  obstructive azoospermia

          -  cryptozoospermia
      </textblock>
